  "title": "Void Renegade",
  "secondName": "Void Renegade",
  "description": "Every thief comes with her own sad story, but Elmina's is especially heinous. Living as a street urchin in Hymelia, the sweet words of a Gru Grimm preacher drew her in. He promised he could numb her pain, erase her history, and give her the power to do as she pleased, as long as she would swear her life to his mysterious god. She did -- and soon came to find that in doing so, she swore away her very free will.\n\nNowadays, she'd sooner swallow coals than follow orders. Sure, not everyone in authority is as evil as the cult that stole her youth, but she isn't taking any more chances. She is more than happy to help her friends -- but she will never spill blood again for what she doesn't believe is right.",
